The evidence with the title 'Level the playing field for trade | U.S. Chamber Of Commerce ' says Aug 15, 2017  ... U.S. goods arriving in foreign markets face an average tariff of 5.9 % , according to the World Economic Forum's latest Global Enabling Trade Report.  ... Face higher tariffs abroad than nearly all our trade competitors .  ... And companies must be allowed to operate on a level playing field when it comes to trade . 
